Mary Ann Pascal https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mary_Ann_Pascal 0 Mary Ann Pascal (born February 4, 1958) is an American actress and business executive. She is known for her role as Samantha "Sam" Booke (later Waters) on the Showtime original comedy series Brothers, and is currently Vice President of Player Development at Wynn Las Vegas.
